<section class="bg-ivory">
  <div class="container-prose py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-[720px]">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-navy-deep text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-[1.2] mb-10">Why Founding Faculty Matter</h2>
      <div class="rule-gold mb-12"></div>
      <div class="prose-editorial text-graphite">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-[1.75] mb-6">Institutions are not remembered simply because they were built.</p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-[1.75] mb-6">They are remembered because exceptional people chose to build them.</p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-[1.75] mb-6">Founding Faculty do more than teach.</p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-[1.75] mb-6">They help establish the academic standards, educational philosophy and culture that future educators inherit.</p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-[1.75] mb-6">For Veterinary Academy International, this is not a symbolic title.</p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-[1.75]">It is a responsibility to help shape the institution from its beginning.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
